title: Hanover field hockey coach Judy Schneider wins No. 500
text: Hanover field hockey coach Judy Schneider wins No. 500 Hanover defeated Pembroke, 1-0, Thursday giving coach Judy Schneider her 500th career victory. Comment Posted Oct. 9, 2015 at 6:46 pm Updated Oct 9, 2015 at 6:58 PM Hanover field hockey coach Judy Schneider notched her 500th victory as her team handed host Pembroke a 1-0 defeat on Friday.
